queries.text:
let ModelName = SemanticModelLogs | where Timestamp between (_startTime .. _endTime) | where ItemName !=''
| summarize arg_max(Timestamp, ItemName) by ItemId
;
let DatasetMode = SemanticModelLogs | where DatasetMode !in ('', 'Unknown')
| summarize arg_max(Timestamp, DatasetMode) by ItemId
;
let total= _baseSMExecutionMetrics 
| summarize TotalCpu=sum(CpuTime), TotalDur=sum(DurTime), TotalCnt=count(), TotalThrottling=countif(capacityThrottling>0);
_baseSMExecutionMetrics
| summarize 
    CPUTime=sum(CpuTime), 
    Max_CPUTime=max(CpuTime), 
    Duration=sum(DurTime), 
    Max_Duration=max(DurTime), 
    OpCnt=count(), 
    Failed=countif(Severity == 2), 
    LogCnt=sum(LogCnt), 
    ThrottlingCnt=countif(capacityThrottling>0), 
    ThrottlingTime=sum(capacityThrottling), 
    EvaluationFrom=min(timeStart), 
    EvaluationTo=max(timeEnd) 
    by CapacityId, ItemId
| extend ['Fail%']= round(100.0*Failed/OpCnt, 1)
| extend ['CPU%']=round(100.0*CPUTime/toscalar (total| project TotalCpu),1)
| extend ['Dur%']=round(100.0*Duration/toscalar (total| project TotalDur),1)
| extend ['Count%']=round(100.0*OpCnt/toscalar (total| project TotalCnt),1)
| extend ['Throttling%']=iff(toscalar (total| project TotalThrottling)==0, toreal(""), round(100.0*ThrottlingCnt/toscalar (total| project TotalThrottling),1))
| extend ItemURL=strcat('https://app.fabric.microsoft.com/datahub/datasets/', ItemId)
| lookup ModelName on ItemId
| lookup DatasetMode on ItemId
| project 
    CapacityId, 
    Mode=DatasetMode, 
    ItemId, 
    ItemName, 
    EvaluationFrom, 
    EvaluationTo, 
    CPUTime, 
    Max_CPUTime, 
    ['CPU%'], 
    Duration, 
    Max_Duration, 
    ['Dur%'], 
    OpCnt, 
    ['Count%'], 
    Failed, 
    ['Fail%'], 
    ThrottlingCnt, 
    ['Throttling%'], 
    ThrottlingTime, 
    LogCnt, 
    ItemURL
| order by CPUTime desc

let Duration=_endTime- _startTime;
let BinSize= case(Duration>= 7d,1d,Duration> 1d,1h,Duration> 6h,10m,Duration > 1h ,1m, 1sec);    //Dynamic display of time bins depending on the Time rage of the query
_baseSMRefresh
| summarize Count=count() by bin(CommandStart, BinSize), DurationBucket

let Duration=_endTime- _startTime;
let BinSize= case(Duration>= 7d,1d,Duration> 1d,1h,Duration> 6h,10m,Duration > 1h ,1m, 1sec);    //Dynamic display of time bins depending on the Time rage of the query
_baseSMQuery 
| summarize Count=count() by bin(Timestamp, BinSize), DurationBucket
| order by DurationBucket asc

let totalQuery= _baseSMQuery
| summarize TotalCpu=sum(CpuTime), TotalDur=sum(DurTime), TotalCnt=count();
let QueryStat = _baseSMQuery
| join kind=leftouter _baseSMExecutionMetrics on OperationId
| summarize CpuTime=sum(CpuTime), AvgCpu=round(avg(CpuTime),1), MaxCpu=max(CpuTime), Duration=sum(DurTime), AvgDur=round(avg(DurTime),1), MaxDur=max(DurTime), Cnt=count(), Failed=countif(Severity == 2), Users=dcount(effectiveClaims), ThrottlingCnt=countif(capacityThrottling>0), ThrottlingSec=sum(capacityThrottling) by ItemId;
QueryStat 
| extend ['Failed%']= round(100.0*Failed/Cnt, 1)
| extend ['CPU%']=round(100.0*CpuTime/toscalar (totalQuery| project TotalCpu),1)
| extend ['Dur%']=round(100.0*Duration/toscalar (totalQuery| project TotalDur),1)
| extend ['Count%']=round(100.0*Cnt/toscalar (totalQuery| project TotalCnt),1)
| extend ['Thrl%']=round(100.0*ThrottlingCnt/ Cnt,1)
| project ItemId, Users, Cnt, Failed, ['Failed%'], ['Count%'], CpuTime, AvgCpu, MaxCpu, ['CPU%'], Duration, AvgDur, MaxDur, ['Dur%'], ThrottlingCnt, ThrottlingSec, ['Thrl%']
| extend ItemURL=strcat('https://app.fabric.microsoft.com/datahub/datasets/', ItemId)
| order by CpuTime desc

let totalRefresh= _baseSMRefresh
| summarize TotalCpu=sum(CpuTime), TotalDur=sum(DurTime), TotalCnt=count();
let ProgressStat = _baseSMProgress
| summarize Tables=dcountif(TableName, TableName !=''), Partitions=dcountif(strcat(TableName, PartitionName), PartitionTMID !=''), PartitionTMID=dcountif(PartitionTMID, PartitionTMID !='') by ItemId
;
let RefreshStat = _baseSMRefresh
| summarize CpuTime=sum(CpuTime), AvgCpu=round(avg(CpuTime),1), MaxCpu=max(CpuTime), Duration=sum(DurTime), AvgDur=round(avg(DurTime),1), MaxDur=max(DurTime), Cnt=count(), Failed=countif(Severity == 2) by ItemId;
RefreshStat
| lookup ProgressStat on ItemId
| extend ['Failed%']= round(100.0*Failed/Cnt, 1)
| extend ['CPU%']=round(100.0*CpuTime/toscalar (totalRefresh| project TotalCpu),1)
| extend ['Dur%']=round(100.0*Duration/toscalar (totalRefresh| project TotalDur),1)
| extend ['Count%']=round(100.0*Cnt/toscalar (totalRefresh| project TotalCnt),1)
| project ItemId, Tables, Partitions, Cnt, Failed, ['Failed%'], ['Count%'], CpuTime, AvgCpu, MaxCpu, ['CPU%'], Duration, AvgDur, MaxDur, ['Dur%'], PartitionTMID
| extend ItemURL=strcat('https://app.fabric.microsoft.com/datahub/datasets/', ItemId)
| order by CpuTime desc

_baseSMRefresh
| summarize Cnt=count() by Status

let totalRefresh= _baseSMRefresh
| summarize TotalCpu=sum(CpuTime), TotalDur=sum(DurTime), TotalCnt=count();
let ProgressStat = _baseSMProgress
| summarize TableTMID=max(TableTMID), PartitionTMID=max(PartitionTMID), Partition=max(PartitionName), RowCount=max(ProgressCounter) by CorrelationId, OperationId, XmlaObjectPath, ObjectType, ItemId
| extend Partition=strcat(TableTMID, Partition)
| summarize Tables=dcountif(TableTMID, TableTMID !=''), Partitions=dcountif(Partition, PartitionTMID !=''), PartitionTMID=dcountif(PartitionTMID, PartitionTMID !=''), RowProcessed=sum(RowCount), Hierarchies=dcountif(XmlaObjectPath, ObjectType =='Hierarchy') by ItemId
;
let RefreshStat = _baseSMRefresh
| summarize CpuTime=sum(CpuTime), AvgCpu=round(avg(CpuTime),1), MaxCpu=max(CpuTime), Duration=sum(DurTime), AvgDur=round(avg(DurTime),1), MaxDur=max(DurTime), Cnt=count(), Failed=countif(Severity == 2) by ItemId;
RefreshStat
| lookup ProgressStat on ItemId
| extend ['Failed%']= round(100.0*Failed/Cnt, 1)
| extend ['CPU%']=round(100.0*CpuTime/toscalar (totalRefresh| project TotalCpu),1)
| extend ['Dur%']=round(100.0*Duration/toscalar (totalRefresh| project TotalDur),1)
| extend ['Count%']=round(100.0*Cnt/toscalar (totalRefresh| project TotalCnt),1)
| project ItemId, Tables, Partitions, Hierarchies, Cnt, Failed, ['Failed%'], ['Count%'], CpuTime, AvgCpu, MaxCpu, ['CPU%'], Duration, AvgDur, MaxDur, ['Dur%'], PartitionTMID
| extend ItemURL=strcat('https://app.powerbi.com/datahub/datasets/', ItemId)
| order by CpuTime desc

let PartitionColumn = _baseSMProgress | where OperationDetailName == 'CompressSegment'
| summarize ColumnCount=dcount(oii) by TableName, PartitionName, OperationId;
_baseSMProgress
| where OperationDetailName != 'CompressSegment' and ObjectType == 'Partition'
| summarize arg_min(ProgressStart=Timestamp, OperationId, OperationDetailName, TableName, PartitionName, TableTMID, PartitionTMID), arg_max(ProgressEnd=Timestamp, Status, DurTime, CpuTime, MashupCPUTime, MashupPeakMemory), RowProcessed=max(ProgressCounter), StatusCode=min(StatusCode), ErrorHex=max(ErrorHex), ExecuteSqlStart=minif(Timestamp, OperationDetailName == 'ExecuteSql'), ExecuteSql=maxif(DurTime, OperationDetailName == 'ExecuteSql'), ExecuteSqlEnd=maxif(Timestamp, OperationDetailName == 'ExecuteSql' and OperationName == 'ProgressReportEnd'), ReadDataStart=minif(Timestamp, OperationDetailName == 'ReadData'), ReadData=maxif(DurTime, OperationDetailName == 'ReadData'), ReadDataSec=maxif(DurationMs, OperationDetailName == 'ReadData')/1000, ReadDataEnd=maxif(Timestamp, OperationDetailName == 'ReadData' and OperationName == 'ProgressReportEnd'), LastReadData=maxif(Timestamp, OperationDetailName == 'ReadData') by CorrelationId
| join kind=leftouter PartitionColumn on TableName, PartitionName, OperationId
| project OperationId, CorrelationId, OperationDetailName, TableName, PartitionName, ProgressStart, DurTime, ExecuteSql, ReadData, ['Row/Sec']=RowProcessed/ReadDataSec, RowProcessed, ColumnCount, ProgressEnd, CpuTime, MashupCPUTime, MashupPeakMemory, ExecuteSqlStart, ExecuteSqlEnd, ReadDataStart, ReadDataEnd, Status, ErrorHex, StatusCode
| extend Severity=iif(ErrorHex !='', 2, iif(Status !='Succeeded', 3, 4))
| extend Status=iif(ErrorHex !='', 'Failed', Status)
| where Status has _status
| order by ProgressStart desc

_baseSMRefresh 
| summarize Cnt=count() by RequestApp

let Duration=_endTime- _startTime;
let BinSize= case(Duration>= 7d,1d,Duration> 1d,1h,Duration> 6h,10m,Duration > 1h ,1m, 1sec);    //Dynamic display of time bins depending on the Time rage of the query
_baseSMExecutionMetrics
| summarize CpuTime=sum(CpuTime) by bin(timeStart, BinSize), commandType

let Duration=_endTime- _startTime;
let BinSize= case(Duration>= 7d,1d,Duration> 1d,1h,Duration> 6h,10m,Duration > 1h ,1m, 1sec);    //Dynamic display of time bins depending on the Time rage of the query
_baseSMExecutionMetrics
| extend timeStart=timeStart+totimespan(_utcOffset)
| summarize ThrlTime=sum(capacityThrottling), ThrlCnt=countif(capacityThrottling > 0) by bin(timeStart, BinSize)

_baseSMQuery
| summarize Cnt=count() by Status

_baseSMQuery
| summarize Cnt=count() by RequestApp

_baseSMExecutionMetrics | project-away CpuTimeMs, DurationMs //to use the duarton and cpu from the engine for sorting
| join kind=inner (_baseSMQuery | project OperationId, DurationMs, CpuTimeMs) on OperationId | project-away OperationId1
| top 1000 by column_ifexists(_OrderBy, timeStart) desc

_baseSMQuery
| lookup (_baseSMExecutionMetrics | project OperationId, PeakMem, capacityThrottling) on OperationId
| top 5000 by column_ifexists(_OrderBy, Timestamp) desc

let totalQuery= _baseSMQuery
| summarize TotalCpu=sum(CpuTime), TotalDur=sum(DurTime), TotalCnt=count();
let QueryStat = _baseSMQuery
| join kind=leftouter _baseSMExecutionMetrics on OperationId
| summarize CpuTime=sum(CpuTime), AvgCpu=round(avg(CpuTime),1), MaxCpu=max(CpuTime), DurTime=sum(DurTime), AvgDur=round(avg(DurTime),1), MaxDur=max(DurTime), Cnt=count(), Failed=countif(Severity == 2), Users=dcount(effectiveClaims), ThrottlingCnt=countif(capacityThrottling>0), ThrottlingTime=sum(capacityThrottling), PeakMemory=max(PeakMem), Report=dcountif(ReplicaId, ReportId !=''), Dataset=dcountif(DatasetId, DatasetId !=''), VisualId=dcountif(VisualId, VisualId !='') by ItemId;
QueryStat 
| extend ['Failed%']= round(100.0*Failed/Cnt, 1)
| extend ['CPU%']=round(100.0*CpuTime/toscalar (totalQuery| project TotalCpu),1)
| extend ['Dur%']=round(100.0*DurTime/toscalar (totalQuery| project TotalDur),1)
| extend ['Count%']=round(100.0*Cnt/toscalar (totalQuery| project TotalCnt),1)
| extend ['Thrl%']=round(100.0*ThrottlingCnt/ Cnt,1)
| project ItemId, Users, Dataset, Report, VisualId, Cnt, Failed, ['Failed%'], ['Count%'], CpuTime, AvgCpu, MaxCpu, ['CPU%'], DurTime, AvgDur, MaxDur, ['Dur%'], ThrottlingCnt, ThrottlingTime, ['Thrl%'], PeakMemory
| extend ItemURL=strcat('https://app.powerbi.com/datahub/datasets/', ItemId)
| order by CpuTime desc

_baseSMProgress
| where OperationId == _operationId
| where OperationDetailName == 'ReadData'
| project Timestamp, Partition=strcat(TableName, '|', PartitionName), RowCount=ProgressCounter

_baseSMProgress
| where OperationId == _operationId
| project-reorder Timestamp, CorrelationId, TableName, PartitionName, ObjectType, ObjectName, Status, StatusCode, DurTime, CpuTime, ProgressCounter, OperationName, OperationDetailName, EventText, Severity
| order by Timestamp asc

let ConvertIntendedUsage = (enum: int) { case(enum == 0, 'Default', enum == 1, 'Scheduled', enum == 2, 'Interactive', enum == 3, 'Service', 'NA') };
_baseSMExecutionMetrics
| join kind=inner (_baseSMRefresh | project OperationId, DurationMs, CpuTimeMs) on OperationId
| project ItemId, OperationId, intendedUsage, commandType, timeStart, DurTime, CpuTime, PeakMem, timeEnd, refreshParallelism, qsoReplicaVersion, errorCount, queryDialect, externalQueryExecutionTime, queryProcessingCpuTime, tabularConnectionTimeout, executionDelay, vertipaqJobCpuTime, mEngineCpuTime, mEnginePeakMemory, vertipaqTotalRows, discoverType, LogCnt, CapacityId, Severity, DurationMs, CpuTimeMs
| order by column_ifexists(_OrderBy, timeStart)

| summarize TableTMID=max(TableTMID), PartitionTMID=max(PartitionTMID), Partition=max(PartitionName), RowCount=max(ProgressCounter) by CorrelationId, OperationId, XmlaObjectPath, ObjectType
| extend Partition=strcat(TableTMID, Partition)
| summarize Tables=dcountif(TableTMID, TableTMID !=''), Partitions=dcountif(Partition, PartitionTMID !=''), PartitionTMID=dcountif(PartitionTMID, PartitionTMID !=''), RowProcessed=sum(RowCount), Hierarchies=dcountif(XmlaObjectPath, ObjectType =='Hierarchy') by OperationId
;

| order by column_ifexists(_OrderBy, CommandStart)

|extend Table=iff(isnotempty( TableName), TableName, Table)
|where Table !startswith "$" and isnotempty( Table)
|distinct Table
|order by Table asc ;
let tables2=EventhouseDataOperationLogs
|where TableName !startswith "$" and isnotempty( TableName)
|distinct Table=TableName
;
union tables1, tables2
|distinct Table
|order by Table asc
